Taron Kolin kasashe takwas masu arzikin masanaÊ¼antu na (G8), ya shirya sanya batun karfafa samar da abinchi a nahiyar Afirka kan ajandar zaman taron da zaÊ¼a yi a nan Amurka.

Shugaban Amurka Barack Obama, shi ya bada shawarar saka batun kan ajandar taron a matsayinsa na shugaban kasar dake daukan nauyin zaman taron kolin na G8.
Matsalar fari na yawaita janyo rashin isassehn kayan abinchi a nahiyar Afirka duk da agajin miliyoyin Dalolin da ake turawa Afirka kowaced shekara.

Kasashen kudu maso gabashin Afirka sun fi fuskanta kamfar ruwa a shekarar da ta gabata, sai mkuma Somalia inda a yanzu ake fama da rashin kayan abinchi.
Kazalika akwai wasu kasashen dake fama da wannan matsalar a yankin Yammacin Afirka.

